<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/path/to/your/css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1><%= title %></h1>
    </header>
    <main>
        <section>
            <p>
                Oops, something went wrong!
            </p>
            <div>
                <%- message %> <!-- Unescaped EJS block for rendering the error message -->
            </div>
            <p>But don’t worry, it’s not the end of the world!</p>
            <p>Here’s a fun fact to lighten the mood: Did you know that sloths can hold their breath longer than dolphins?</p>
        </section>
        <section>
            <a href="/">Return to the homepage</a>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
